There were 2 people with a wish
2 Live a life full of LOVE
2 GOD would pray that they would stay together
under the stars above
But someone else made a wish.
at the same time in the same breath
And although wish 4 love was granted
So was this wicked wish 4 Death
Now i make a wish
sealed with tears and laughter
It is my wish that these 2 loves
R reunited in the afterlife
